snippet.title: Gravity Fighters - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
https://wychwaystudios.itch.io/gravity-fighters
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.wychwaystudios.gravityfighters

Space battles for 1-4 players.  Harness the power of gravity!  Fire projectiles around destructible solar systems and be the last one standing.  Two different modes, 1-4 players and endless customisable solar systems to fight in.

Available on Google Play, and soon for PC.
